Step 4 - Open deeper.zip (password: ghost)

    unzip -P ghost deeper.zip
    # extracts: carrier.jpg, mystery.pdf, final.jpg

The password "ghost" matches the challenge title "FIND THE GHOST" and was findable by
trying theme-related words.

